reviews.text: Staff here are always very helpful and friendly
Aah great coffee at 2 am

As I checked out of my hotel long time before my flight, I took my small suitcase walked to the harbor, took some photos, and then wanted to chill, work on my laptop till the time of my flight. The night before I was inn Macau, sadly didn't find a souvenir that said Macau on it, so the cool thing in this branch is that I found these mini Starbucks mugs that said Macau on it, others that said China & Hong Kong as well. Oh and they had a promotion where I buy a drink and get the 2nd one for free :)
nice environment
Starbucks is a Starbucks... What do you expect?...
